i\" /><br />\n仲話用汔油車去爆班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我敢話推post 班友一係就係中共五毛, 想殺狗祭旗<br />\n一係就係白痴on9狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家中五手足俾狗射到, 班狗都要解釋一大輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果有手足係夢境舉高支架生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班狗係可以大條道理十人連射shot to kill<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班狗係等左呢一刻好撚耐!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時死既唔單止係舉架生既手足<br />\n後邊既手足仲會一齊陪葬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n私底下你地用黎切牛扒, 切西瓜, 切乜切物無人會話你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係夢境一定千祈唔可以拎架生出去!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n切記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0e589f14f8328695ecdc3414e335eb5d7c045d","tid":1611671,"uid":28575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"去遊行就唔帶刀既，帶左佢下次開槍藉口都唔洗諗。不過你私底下行街接收工帶就冇人理"},{"pid":"c60e410d6372bc959d57f631a97b11f6713c755a","tid":1611671,"uid":321906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:34:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c03d72ce944e986059758addda07117d8f1d4e4","tid":1611671,"uid":57,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgm